!TITLE
QUICK-QUOTE: PRESIDENTIAL PROMISES
!WORDS
"Then [President Clinton] said he wanted to help me with the 
Scientology situation in Germany. He said he had a roommate years ago 
who was a Scientologist and had really liked him and respected his 
views on it.  He said he felt we were given an unfair hand in that 
country, and that he wanted to fix it."
          --Actor and Scientologist John Travolta, after meeting Bill 
Clinton last spring (quoted in Time,
                            Sep 22, 1997, page 20)
